   <text>
      <front>
         <pb/>
         <milestone n="137" unit="page"/>
         <argument xml:id="ARGUnp">
            <head>
               <lb/>
               <emph>ADVERTISEMENT.</emph>
            </head>
            <p> BY Persons resident in the country and attached to <lb/>rural
                                   objects, many places will be found un-named or of un-<lb/>known
                                   names, where little Incidents will have occurred, or
                                   <lb/>Feelings been experienced, which will have given to such
                                   pla-<lb/>ces a private and peculiar interest. From a wish to give
                                   <lb/>some sort of Record to such Incidents or renew the
                                   gratifi-<lb/>cation of such Feelings, names have been given to
                                   places by <lb/>the Author and some of his friends, and the
                                   following Poems <lb/>written in consequence.</p>
         </argument>
      </front>
      <body>
         <p> </p>
      </body>
